TableDefinition.DatabaseQuery: SELECT wtyp."wtyp-cd-wtyp", wtyp."wtyp-lo-indi", wtyp."wtyp-cd-ext", wbas."wbas-ky", wbas."wbas-lo-indi", wtyp."wtyp-ky", wtyp."wtyp-nr-wtyp", wtyp."wtyp-cd-int", TO_CHAR(wroo."wroo-qt-uurw"), wroo."wroo-cd-part", wfun."ofun-kc", ofun."ofun-om-ofun", ofun."ofun-lo-besc", wfun."okso-kc", okos."okos-nm-okos", worg."obas-kc", worg."oorg-kc", worg."olok-kc", wwer."wwer-cd-emai", wwer."wwer-cd-teli", wbas."wbas-nm-voll", wbas."wbas-om-voor", wbas."wbas-nm-voor", wbas."wbas-nm-init", wbas."wbas-nm-acht", wbas."wbas-nm-tusa", wbas."wbas-cd-burg", wbas."wbas-lo-gesl", wbas."wbas-dw-geb", wbas."wbas-nm-gebl", wbas."wbas-nm-gebp", wpar."wpar-nm-wpar", wpar."wpar-nm-tusv", wpar."wpar-cd-naam", wtax."wtax-cd-sofi", wtyp."wtyp-cd-type", wtyp."wtyp-cd-stat", wrel."wtyp-ky-bwty", wdie."wdie-dw-begi", wdie."wdie-dw-eind" FROM pub.wtyp "wtyp" INNER JOIN pub.wbas "wbas" ON wbas."wbas-ky" = wtyp."wbas-ky" AND wbas."wbas-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wbas."wbas-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wbas."wbas-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wdie "wdie" ON wdie."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wdie."wdie-cd-mut" = 'c' LEFT JOIN pub.wpar "wpar" ON wpar."wbas-ky" = wtyp."wbas-ky" AND wpar."wpar-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wpar."wpar-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wpar."wpar-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wtax "wtax" ON wtax."wbas-ky" = wtyp."wbas-ky" AND wtax."wtax-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wtax."wtax-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wtax."wtax-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wfun "wfun" ON wfun."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wfun."wfun-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wfun."wfun-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wfun."wfun-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wkos "wkos" ON wkos."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wkos."wkos-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wkos."wkos-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wkos."wkos-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.worg "worg" ON worg."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND worg."worg-cd-mut" = 'c' AND worg."worg-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND worg."worg-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wroo "wroo" ON wroo."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wroo."wroo-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wroo."wroo-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wroo."wroo-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wwer "wwer" ON wwer."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wwer."wwer-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wwer."wwer-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wwer."wwer-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.wrel "wrel" ON wrel."wtyp-ky" = wtyp."wtyp-ky" AND wrel."wrel-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wrel."wrel-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wrel."wrel-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.ofun "ofun" ON ofun."ofun-kc" = wfun."ofun-kc" AND ofun."ofun-cd-mut" = 'c' AND ofun."ofun-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND ofun."ofun-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE LEFT JOIN pub.okos "okos" ON okos."okos-kc" = wkos."okos-kc" AND okos."okos-cd-mut" = 'c' AND okos."okos-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND okos."okos-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE WHERE wtyp."wtyp-cd-mut" = 'c' AND wtyp."wtyp-dg-begi" <= SYSDATE + 14 AND wtyp."wtyp-dg-eint" >= SYSDATE AND wtyp."wtyp-cd-ext" = '' ORDER BY wtyp."wtyp-ky", wdie."wdie-dw-begi" DESC, wdie."wdie-dw-eind" DESC
